column5: hi folks my boat is not ready. any chance somebody pull me behind them in a tube?

that makes 2 of us dude. My new boat and motor is sitting in my portable garage on tires...waiting for my new trailer to come in!!! 2 new rods leaning against the wall waiting to be used...walleye just opened up in select parts of the water up here yesterday   . Trailer should be in this week...
